title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Fowles / Leber / St. Aubin / Korzo
description:
The FAN's Eric Nordquist fills in for Paul Allen on this Thursday!

He welcomes Lynx All-Star Sylvia Fowles to the program to talk about her upcoming trips to Las Vegas.

Then, FSN North color commentator Kyndra de St. Aubin goes scarves up with Nordo, before hard-hitting football and baseball segments with Ben Leber and Scott Korzenowski close out the show.
